article_id:2119,category_name:News,title_name:Adding the Mana Spiral to More Adventurers![Update],image_path:,message:<div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1618200000"></span>]</strong></span></div><div>The time around when the mana spiral will be added was incorrectly listed as 04/11/2021 at 10:40 PM PT. It should in fact read 04/11/2021 at 11 PM PT.<br><br>Thank you for your understanding.</div><hr><div>A sixth mana circle, the mana spiral, will be added to certain adventurer starting <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1618207200"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>The adventurer affected this time and her stats are described below.</div><div>Note: Unlocking a 5★ Gala Dragalia adventurer&#39;s mana spiral requires special materials specific to that adventurer that can be earned from the daily bonus of the Trials of the Mighty quest.</div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div>■Affected Adventurers</div><div>5★ Gala Elisanne (water/axe)</div><div><br></div><div>■Stats</div><div><br></div><div>・5★ adventurer</div><div>
